It's this crazy-ass redneck right here.

115
00:08:30,244 --> 00:08:32,380
I guaran-goddamn-tee you,

116
00:08:32,513 --> 00:08:33,781
if it wasn't for him,

117
00:08:34,682 --> 00:08:36,484
